<BR>
What annoy's me is the &quot;techno&quot; look (thats what it is to me) of the site.  As I noted before, the color scheme is totally wrong for a site dedicated to a fantasy based rpg.  the scheme would work well for the Starwars game.  The earth and woodtones you had before were fine.<BR>
I also question your aquiesence to UGO with the branding of the site, I look at the top of the page and what I see would leave me to believe that this site is UGO.  They have a bright colorful logo in the op left corner of the page.  what do you have?  Well slightly to the left you have the site name in PLAIN WHITE block letters.  The we have the now bigger than before but still acceptable banner-ad, and below that in small white block text the fact that this is one of several RPG Lore Network sies and links to the others.  In other words, this site is now an UGO  branded site (ie it looks like they own it.)  <BR>
<BR>
