				Hi everyone - I am one of the site owners.  I understand that the look is totally different now, but please understand that this site is extrememly expensive to run, and we need to get some revenue from somewhere.  Contacting UGO is only going to hurt us and make it harder for us to keep the site running.  I loved the old designs, Georgia did a fantastic job.  But if we want to keep this a free site and keep it up and running this is what we have to do.  We'll keep trying to improve the sites, and hopefully be able to modify the look a bit more soon, but right now we need this to work.  So please, don't send hammering emails to UGO - they didn't force us to do this, it's just that this way we can continue to try and defray some of the site expenses with advertising.<BR>
